#  Telegram Food Ordering Bot

A Telegram-based food ordering system built with **Java 17** and **Spring Boot**.

Users can select food items, enter quantity, and confirm or cancel their orders directly via Telegram.
An Admin REST API is also provided for managing foods and viewing orders with filters.

---

## Features

- Food selection via Telegram Inline Keyboard
- Quantity input via chat messages
- Order confirmation and cancellation
- Order status management (DRAFT, CONFIRMED, CANCELED)
- User session and state management
- Admin REST API for order and food management

---

##  Bot Flow
/start
